reviewText: They sold it as a good horror movie with alot of gore alot of hot chicks and alot of fun.  I would say there is almost no gore and no inventive kills.  None of the women really show off anything beyond a bra and the there were a few places and chances that it would have easily fit.  I think it had everything going for it from the trailer so much that I ordered it but maybe I can save you the trouble don't bother.
